As a Student, I want to log in to the app so I can access my profile.
As a Student, I want to view a home dashboard, so that I can easily navigate to my bookings and doctor list
As a Staff Member (Admin/Doctor), I want to log in securely so I can access the clinic dashboard.
As a Student, I want to check doctor details to choose the right physician.
As a Student, I want to book an appointment to avoid waiting in line.
As a Student, I want to view my appointments to remember my schedule.
As an Admin, I want to manage the schedule so students can see available slots.
As a Doctor, I want to add and edit medical notes to keep patient records updated
As a Patient/Doctor, I want to view medical notes to track treatment history.
